WEBVTT

00:00:11.390 --> 00:00:12.040 line:80%
Guards!

00:00:12.880 --> 00:00:13.440 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:00:13.470 --> 00:00:15.120 line:80%
Punish Yan Zheng alone!

00:00:15.390 --> 00:00:15.920 line:80%
Yes, sir!

00:00:16.670 --> 00:00:18.080 line:80%
-Execute!
-Your Lordship!

00:00:18.080 --> 00:00:19.400 line:80%
My husband really knew nothing about that!

00:00:19.400 --> 00:00:20.260 line:80%
Your Lordship!

00:00:20.830 --> 00:00:22.080 line:80%
My husband knew nothing about that!

00:00:22.080 --> 00:00:22.870 line:80%
-Your Lordship!
-Do it!

00:00:22.870 --> 00:00:23.560 line:80%
Go away!

00:00:23.800 --> 00:00:24.710 line:80%
Wait!

00:00:45.760 --> 00:00:47.440 line:80%
If you want to punish him,
punish me as well.

00:00:47.440 --> 00:00:50.370 line:80%
I share responsibility
for what happened today too!

00:00:51.360 --> 00:00:52.740 line:80%
What responsibility do you have?

00:00:52.740 --> 00:00:53.670 line:80%
Miss Beholden,

00:00:53.700 --> 00:00:55.430 line:80%
this has nothing to do with you!

00:00:55.640 --> 00:00:57.550 line:80%
I was also fully aware that Mrs. Fan

00:00:57.550 --> 00:00:58.880 line:80%
took the prisoner away.

00:00:59.230 --> 00:01:00.640 line:80%
I failed to report it,

00:01:00.640 --> 00:01:01.700 line:80%
so I'm also guilty.

00:01:01.870 --> 00:01:03.530 line:80%
I'm merely a royal physician.

00:01:05.250 --> 00:01:06.910 line:80%
So what if you beat me to death?

00:01:08.120 --> 00:01:09.980 line:80%
These are military regulations.

00:01:11.330 --> 00:01:12.660 line:80%
Military regulations?

00:01:13.000 --> 00:01:14.460 line:80%
Then I should kneel first.

00:01:21.110 --> 00:01:21.839 line:80%
Wait!

00:01:28.480 --> 00:01:29.339 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:01:32.130 --> 00:01:34.210 line:80%
Something has happened in the cave.

00:01:34.589 --> 00:01:36.790 line:80%
Shi Yue brought a few top-tier fighters

00:01:36.950 --> 00:01:37.839 line:80%
and dug through the wall,

00:01:37.839 --> 00:01:39.570 line:80%
trying to rescue Sui Yuanqing.

00:01:39.839 --> 00:01:42.440 line:80%
If Mrs. Fan hadn't happened to
take him away,

00:01:42.470 --> 00:01:45.000 line:80%
that rascal might have already
been rescued.

00:01:46.000 --> 00:01:48.000 line:80%
Although Mrs. Fan

00:01:48.200 --> 00:01:50.800 line:80%
violated military orders
by acting on her own,

00:01:51.029 --> 00:01:52.640 line:80%
she secured the hostage.

00:01:53.600 --> 00:01:54.630 line:80%
In my opinion,

00:01:54.839 --> 00:01:56.830 line:80%
her merits cancel out her faults.

00:01:57.029 --> 00:01:57.950 line:80%
Right, Your Lord...

00:01:57.950 --> 00:01:59.210 line:80%
Right, Your Lordship?

00:02:02.750 --> 00:02:06.110 line:80%
Since the Counselor and the Physician
both plead for leniency,

00:02:06.110 --> 00:02:07.080 line:80%
then...

00:02:07.800 --> 00:02:09.270 line:80%
I'll let you off this time?

00:02:09.710 --> 00:02:10.510 line:80%
Yan Zheng!

00:02:11.880 --> 00:02:14.250 line:80%
What do you think?

00:02:29.160 --> 00:02:30.620 line:80%
Thank you, Your Lordship.

00:02:31.480 --> 00:02:34.540 line:80%
-Thank you, Your Lordship!
-Thank you, Your Lordship!

00:03:59.230 --> 00:04:04.590 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:04:04.710 --> 00:04:07.190 line:80%
[Episode 26]

00:04:08.510 --> 00:04:10.600 line:80%
Mrs. Fan is no ordinary woman.

00:04:10.710 --> 00:04:12.070 line:80%
You should've seen it—

00:04:12.430 --> 00:04:14.160 line:80%
those 50- or 60-catty salt sacks,

00:04:14.160 --> 00:04:15.270 line:80%
she hoisted them onto her shoulders,

00:04:15.270 --> 00:04:16.310 line:80%
four at a time!

00:04:16.670 --> 00:04:17.870 line:80%
Carrying salt sacks in one hand

00:04:17.870 --> 00:04:19.400 line:80%
and a whole roast lamb in the other
while running—

00:04:19.400 --> 00:04:20.670 line:80%
she was still the fastest one!

00:04:20.670 --> 00:04:21.990 line:80%
That valiant, heroic bearing of hers—

00:04:21.990 --> 00:04:24.310 line:80%
she was truly like
a deity descended from heaven!

00:04:24.310 --> 00:04:25.920 line:80%
I also heard that

00:04:26.430 --> 00:04:29.360 line:80%
when Mrs. Fan was hauling bricks
at the Wu River camp,

00:04:29.430 --> 00:04:31.160 line:80%
she carried 300 catties all by herself

00:04:31.160 --> 00:04:32.360 line:80%
-in one go!
-How much?

00:04:32.400 --> 00:04:33.670 line:80%
Three hundred catties?

00:04:33.670 --> 00:04:34.830 line:80%
Who told you that?

00:04:35.550 --> 00:04:37.400 line:80%
Each basket weighed 300 catties,

00:04:37.400 --> 00:04:38.990 line:80%
and she could carry two baskets.

00:04:38.990 --> 00:04:40.230 line:80%
That's 600 catties!

00:04:40.520 --> 00:04:42.070 line:80%
-Six hundred catties?
-Six hundred catties?

00:04:42.070 --> 00:04:43.800 line:80%
Can anyone really be that strong?

00:04:43.800 --> 00:04:44.900 line:80%
I recognize you.

00:04:45.070 --> 00:04:47.840 line:80%
You're the ones who earned merits
alongside Mrs. Fan—

00:04:47.840 --> 00:04:48.870 line:80%
the Pig Squad.

00:04:49.840 --> 00:04:51.400 line:80%
The Pig Butcher Squad.

00:04:51.800 --> 00:04:53.630 line:80%
Right, the Pig Butcher Squad!

00:04:54.030 --> 00:04:55.390 line:80%
-Come on, come on!
-Dude, have a seat.

00:04:55.390 --> 00:04:56.250 line:80%
-Sit.
-Come on, dude.

00:04:56.250 --> 00:04:57.790 line:80%
-Come on.
-Have a seat.

00:05:00.230 --> 00:05:01.560 line:80%
Speaking of that night,

00:05:02.130 --> 00:05:03.330 line:80%
it was a moonless, windy night.

00:05:03.330 --> 00:05:04.790 line:80%
Mrs. Fan suddenly noticed

00:05:04.800 --> 00:05:06.490 line:80%
something strange outside the camp.

00:05:06.490 --> 00:05:08.900 line:80%
Suddenly, with a bang, she kicked

00:05:08.930 --> 00:05:10.110 line:80%
open that wooden door

00:05:10.110 --> 00:05:12.520 line:80%
locked with iron chains.

00:05:12.520 --> 00:05:13.960 line:80%
Mrs. Fan

00:05:14.310 --> 00:05:16.970 line:80%
kicked the camp gate open in one kick.

00:05:17.070 --> 00:05:19.070 line:80%
chased for 10 miles alone on horseback,

00:05:19.070 --> 00:05:20.040 line:80%
and killed that scout!

00:05:20.040 --> 00:05:22.160 line:80%
She kicked open the big iron gate
of the military camp

00:05:22.160 --> 00:05:23.870 line:80%
and ran 80 miles without stopping.

00:05:23.870 --> 00:05:25.070 line:80%
With swift, decisive strikes,

00:05:25.070 --> 00:05:26.870 line:80%
she returned
with the heads of three enemy scouts!

00:05:26.870 --> 00:05:28.630 line:80%
Mrs. Fan used to be

00:05:28.670 --> 00:05:30.040 line:80%
a butcher.

00:05:30.230 --> 00:05:31.230 line:80%
Everyone in Lin'an Town

00:05:31.230 --> 00:05:32.400 line:80%
knows her.

00:05:33.160 --> 00:05:34.550 line:80%
With one slap,

00:05:34.550 --> 00:05:37.230 line:80%
she could knock a big fat pig out cold!

00:05:37.920 --> 00:05:39.630 line:80%
Back in those days,

00:05:39.750 --> 00:05:41.380 line:80%
she was valiant and heroic.

00:05:41.520 --> 00:05:42.959 line:80%
When fighting bandits,

00:05:43.040 --> 00:05:44.520 line:80%
she could take on 100 enemies alone

00:05:44.520 --> 00:05:46.040 line:80%
without losing ground.

00:05:46.040 --> 00:05:47.920 line:80%
She once kicked open the city gate.

00:05:47.920 --> 00:05:49.980 line:80%
Even thousands of bandits at the gate

00:05:49.980 --> 00:05:51.520 line:80%
were no match for her alone.

00:05:51.520 --> 00:05:53.870 line:80%
She charged alone into Shi Hu's camp,

00:05:53.959 --> 00:05:55.070 line:80%
carrying four sacks of salt,

00:05:55.070 --> 00:05:56.910 line:80%
five sacks of rice,
six baskets of vegetables,

00:05:56.910 --> 00:05:58.740 line:80%
and four roasted whole lambs—

00:05:58.840 --> 00:05:59.990 line:80%
moving as if no one could stop her!

00:05:59.990 --> 00:06:01.070 line:80%
I also heard

00:06:01.070 --> 00:06:03.330 line:80%
she once killed a bear with a single slap!

00:06:04.480 --> 00:06:07.160 line:80%
One capable woman is worth ten men.

00:06:07.190 --> 00:06:08.430 line:80%
She is truly capable.

00:06:08.560 --> 00:06:10.510 line:80%
Her husband is a lucky guy.

00:06:10.550 --> 00:06:11.630 line:80%
But I heard

00:06:11.690 --> 00:06:14.070 line:80%
her husband is seriously injured
this time.

00:06:14.070 --> 00:06:15.840 line:80%
He's been coughing up blood.

00:06:15.990 --> 00:06:17.980 line:80%
He might not make it.

00:06:18.070 --> 00:06:18.960 line:80%
He's dying.

00:06:19.140 --> 00:06:20.910 line:80%
They've already moved him
into a private tent.

00:06:20.910 --> 00:06:23.750 line:80%
Even if he doesn't die,
he won't be in good shape.

00:06:23.960 --> 00:06:26.560 line:80%
No wonder Mrs. Fan only grabbed meat
this time.

00:06:26.800 --> 00:06:29.530 line:80%
Looks like she's making her husband's
last meal.

00:06:29.990 --> 00:06:32.450 line:80%
She's truly loyal and devoted.

00:06:59.480 --> 00:07:00.190 line:80%
Sister.

00:07:01.960 --> 00:07:03.880 line:80%
You came following the smell, didn't you?

00:07:03.880 --> 00:07:04.870 line:80%
The lamb soup will be ready in a bit.

00:07:04.870 --> 00:07:06.040 line:80%
I'll get you a bowl.

00:07:09.360 --> 00:07:11.630 line:80%
Where are your big brother
and his goofy crew?

00:07:11.630 --> 00:07:14.810 line:80%
While... they're away,

00:07:15.720 --> 00:07:17.380 line:80%
I have something to say to you.

00:07:17.400 --> 00:07:18.160 line:80%
Well...

00:07:19.400 --> 00:07:19.990 line:80%
Go ahead.

00:07:21.360 --> 00:07:22.670 line:80%
I heard...

00:07:22.670 --> 00:07:23.430 line:80%
Changyu!

00:07:23.840 --> 00:07:24.840 line:80%
You're cooking?

00:07:25.140 --> 00:07:26.570 line:80%
Beholden, you came at the right time.

00:07:26.570 --> 00:07:27.430 line:80%
The lamb soup will be ready in a bit.

00:07:27.430 --> 00:07:28.280 line:80%
I'll serve you a bowl.

00:07:28.280 --> 00:07:28.840 line:80%
Okay.

00:07:29.780 --> 00:07:30.570 line:80%
Go ahead.

00:07:30.970 --> 00:07:31.970 line:80%
It smells so good.

00:07:37.040 --> 00:07:38.280 line:80%
This boy...

00:07:38.840 --> 00:07:39.720 line:80%
Changyu,

00:07:40.400 --> 00:07:43.600 line:80%
I heard you once kicked open a city gate
with a single kick?

00:07:43.990 --> 00:07:46.550 line:80%
Who could possibly kick open a city gate
with just one kick?

00:07:46.550 --> 00:07:47.800 line:80%
I also heard...

00:07:47.920 --> 00:07:49.430 line:80%
heard that you snatched the mutton

00:07:49.430 --> 00:07:51.830 line:80%
just to make the last meal
for your husband.

00:07:53.040 --> 00:07:54.230 line:80%
They're just making things up.

00:07:54.230 --> 00:07:55.070 line:80%
Don't listen to them.

00:07:55.070 --> 00:07:56.400 line:80%
They made all that up?

00:07:56.550 --> 00:07:59.230 line:80%
If those rumors reach
the Marquis of Wu'an,

00:07:59.360 --> 00:08:02.360 line:80%
I'm afraid he might
have those people's heads cut off.

00:08:03.840 --> 00:08:05.570 line:80%
He wouldn't go that far, right?

00:08:05.670 --> 00:08:06.920 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an,

00:08:07.400 --> 00:08:09.060 line:80%
aside from a slight stutter,

00:08:09.600 --> 00:08:12.340 line:80%
seems to have a good temper.

00:08:12.600 --> 00:08:15.070 line:80%
He didn't make things hard
for my husband and me, after all.

00:08:15.070 --> 00:08:15.720 line:80%
I don't

00:08:15.750 --> 00:08:18.070 line:80%
have anything fancy to repay him with.

00:08:18.190 --> 00:08:19.400 line:80%
So I made some

00:08:19.400 --> 00:08:20.990 line:80%
lamb soup, stew,

00:08:21.110 --> 00:08:21.920 line:80%
and stir-fry.

00:08:21.920 --> 00:08:23.650 line:80%
Later, help me take them to him.

00:08:25.040 --> 00:08:28.570 line:80%
So you don't hold a grudge against
the Marquis of Wu'an anymore?

00:08:28.670 --> 00:08:30.190 line:80%
How could I hold a grudge?

00:08:30.520 --> 00:08:32.410 line:80%
Every trade has its rules.

00:08:32.430 --> 00:08:33.670 line:80%
Even we butchers

00:08:33.800 --> 00:08:36.060 line:80%
have rules about not giving away extras—

00:08:36.160 --> 00:08:37.800 line:80%
let alone in the army.

00:08:38.469 --> 00:08:40.670 line:80%
I acted on my own this time.

00:08:40.950 --> 00:08:42.750 line:80%
Luckily, reinforcements came.

00:08:42.800 --> 00:08:43.930 line:80%
If they hadn't come,

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:46.470 line:80%
I would've died along with that bastard.

00:08:46.640 --> 00:08:48.350 line:80%
It really wouldn't have been worth it.

00:08:48.350 --> 00:08:49.240 line:80%
Next time,

00:08:49.480 --> 00:08:50.800 line:80%
I'll definitely follow orders

00:08:50.800 --> 00:08:52.800 line:80%
and strike wherever I'm ordered to!

00:08:54.890 --> 00:08:57.090 line:80%
It must've taken him several lifetimes

00:08:57.890 --> 00:09:00.030 line:80%
of luck to deserve a wife like you.

00:09:00.830 --> 00:09:02.000 line:80%
Come on, let me help you.

00:09:02.000 --> 00:09:02.550 line:80%
Here.

00:09:02.830 --> 00:09:04.150 line:80%
Let me serve you a bowl to taste it.

00:09:04.150 --> 00:09:04.790 line:80%
Okay.

00:09:05.430 --> 00:09:05.920 line:80%
Here.

00:09:05.920 --> 00:09:06.400 line:80%
Here.

00:09:08.000 --> 00:09:08.760 line:80%
See if the seasoning's right.

00:09:08.760 --> 00:09:09.280 line:80%
Okay.

00:09:08.930 --> 00:09:11.350 line:80%
[Xie]

00:09:13.550 --> 00:09:14.190 line:80%
Yan Zheng?

00:09:19.200 --> 00:09:19.870 line:80%
Eat up.

00:09:20.400 --> 00:09:21.730 line:80%
It'll help you recover.

00:09:22.350 --> 00:09:23.410 line:80%
Aren't you eating?

00:09:23.900 --> 00:09:26.560 line:80%
I couldn't resist
while I was cooking earlier.

00:09:26.590 --> 00:09:27.790 line:80%
I already ate my fill.

00:09:52.550 --> 00:09:54.700 line:80%
Your injuries haven't fully healed yet.

00:09:53.230 --> 00:09:55.450 line:80%
♪ The scenery is as clear as me ♪

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:56.250 line:80%
You have to eat more.

00:09:56.500 --> 00:09:57.700 line:80%
♪ With very pale colors ♪

00:09:57.410 --> 00:09:58.540 line:80%
To help you recover.

00:09:58.760 --> 00:10:01.420 line:80%
♪ Just like the outline in the mirror ♪

00:10:01.910 --> 00:10:04.500 line:80%
♪ I think that's me, being naive ♪

00:10:05.160 --> 00:10:06.710 line:80%
♪ Unlocking my heart ♪

00:10:07.320 --> 00:10:11.560 line:80%
♪ I hid you in my soul ♪

00:10:14.870 --> 00:10:17.540 line:80%
♪ The moon is as quiet as me ♪

00:10:18.160 --> 00:10:19.940 line:80%
♪ The light shines ♪

00:10:19.630 --> 00:10:20.730 line:80%
Today...

00:10:20.460 --> 00:10:23.240 line:80%
♪ It illuminates
the turbulence in my heart ♪

00:10:21.360 --> 00:10:23.220 line:80%
the Marquis of Wu'an punished us.

00:10:23.240 --> 00:10:24.310 line:80%
Aren't you angry?

00:10:23.630 --> 00:10:26.370 line:80%
♪ It seems to be the fire of love ♪

00:10:25.830 --> 00:10:27.190 line:80%
The Marquis was right to reprimand us.

00:10:26.810 --> 00:10:28.820 line:80%
♪ Just a few sparks ♪

00:10:28.390 --> 00:10:29.880 line:80%
The Pig Butcher Squad and I

00:10:29.150 --> 00:10:34.120 line:80%
♪ Let me hide in your heart ♪

00:10:30.400 --> 00:10:32.230 line:80%
managed to return safely this time

00:10:32.230 --> 00:10:33.690 line:80%
only because we got lucky.

00:10:35.000 --> 00:10:37.920 line:80%
Later, I'll go ask Mr. Gongsun
about the military regulations.

00:10:36.370 --> 00:10:37.660 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love ♪

00:10:37.690 --> 00:10:40.380 line:80%
♪ Will never end ♪

00:10:38.050 --> 00:10:40.070 line:80%
I promise I won't make
the same mistake again.

00:10:40.070 --> 00:10:40.800 line:80%
Also,

00:10:40.800 --> 00:10:41.970 line:80%
♪ It's worth my foolishly waiting ♪

00:10:40.820 --> 00:10:42.660 line:80%
if the Marquis of Wu'an
wants to punish you again,

00:10:41.990 --> 00:10:44.430 line:80%
♪ For a lifetime ♪

00:10:42.760 --> 00:10:43.960 line:80%
tell him to come to me.

00:10:44.000 --> 00:10:45.160 line:80%
You're injured.

00:10:45.010 --> 00:10:48.940 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

00:10:45.190 --> 00:10:46.710 line:80%
You can't take any more punishment.

00:10:46.710 --> 00:10:47.840 line:80%
I can take a beating.

00:10:49.380 --> 00:10:53.210 line:80%
♪ So what if we encounter difficulties? ♪

00:10:52.310 --> 00:10:53.240 line:80%
You've changed.

00:10:53.870 --> 00:10:54.760 line:80%
♪ I pray that our love ♪

00:10:54.670 --> 00:10:55.940 line:80%
Back in Lin'an,

00:10:54.780 --> 00:10:57.370 line:80%
♪ Will not be like sand
slipping into the sea ♪

00:10:55.970 --> 00:10:58.500 line:80%
you would never have
admitted you were wrong.

00:10:58.540 --> 00:10:59.550 line:80%
♪ I'd rather use this life ♪

00:10:59.580 --> 00:11:02.050 line:80%
♪ To guard our love forever ♪

00:11:00.710 --> 00:11:02.310 line:80%
After going through so much,

00:11:02.510 --> 00:11:06.680 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet as me ♪

00:11:02.590 --> 00:11:04.400 line:80%
how could I still be
that simple butcher girl

00:11:04.400 --> 00:11:07.000 line:80%
who only knew
how to butcher pigs and sell meat?

00:11:07.050 --> 00:11:17.660 line:80%
♪ Why do we need
to seek cause and effect ♪

00:11:08.120 --> 00:11:10.470 line:80%
As long as I get to
beat that bastard Sui Yuanqing

00:11:10.470 --> 00:11:11.930 line:80%
as much as I want in the end,

00:11:12.310 --> 00:11:14.440 line:80%
I can follow any military regulation.

00:11:16.410 --> 00:11:18.060 line:80%
Okay. I promise you.

00:11:20.190 --> 00:11:21.310 line:80%
You promise me?

00:11:21.330 --> 00:11:22.670 line:80%
It's not like you have any say here.

00:11:22.520 --> 00:11:27.140 line:80%
♪ Clear and quiet ♪

00:11:23.080 --> 00:11:24.320 line:80%
Whatever you say,

00:11:25.350 --> 00:11:26.640 line:80%
I'll agree to it.

00:11:28.890 --> 00:11:35.130 line:80%
♪ As me ♪

00:11:33.550 --> 00:11:36.550 line:80%
You need to drink this herbal medicine
while it's hot.

00:11:38.440 --> 00:11:39.110 line:80%
By the way,

00:11:39.670 --> 00:11:42.470 line:80%
I met an old gentleman
when I was working on the dam.

00:11:43.070 --> 00:11:45.640 line:80%
He had a sharp tongue but a soft heart.

00:11:45.800 --> 00:11:46.830 line:80%
To save me,

00:11:47.280 --> 00:11:50.040 line:80%
he even swapped
his life-and-death lot with mine.

00:11:50.040 --> 00:11:51.070 line:80%
Since he helped you,

00:11:51.070 --> 00:11:53.470 line:80%
we'll just promote him
when the time comes.

00:11:54.720 --> 00:11:56.180 line:80%
How could you promote him?

00:12:07.560 --> 00:12:08.950 line:80%
I mean...

00:12:10.590 --> 00:12:11.390 line:80%
in the future.

00:12:12.710 --> 00:12:14.350 line:80%
Are you that confident

00:12:14.830 --> 00:12:16.690 line:80%
you'll become a general someday?

00:12:29.520 --> 00:12:30.670 line:80%
What if—

00:12:31.830 --> 00:12:33.040 line:80%
I mean, what if—

00:12:35.670 --> 00:12:37.000 line:80%
what if in the future,

00:12:37.000 --> 00:12:39.660 line:80%
I become an official
even higher than a general?

00:12:39.970 --> 00:12:40.990 line:80%
Like what?

00:12:43.320 --> 00:12:44.470 line:80%
Like...

00:12:45.930 --> 00:12:47.590 line:80%
being made a marquis or a lord?

00:12:50.400 --> 00:12:52.770 line:80%
A marquis or a lord?

00:12:55.190 --> 00:12:56.920 line:80%
Then wouldn't I, a butcher,

00:12:57.070 --> 00:12:58.670 line:80%
become a marchioness?

00:13:00.000 --> 00:13:01.130 line:80%
Would you want that?

00:13:02.000 --> 00:13:03.000 line:80%
Of course I would.

00:13:03.020 --> 00:13:05.350 line:80%
Only a fool would refuse
such a good thing.

00:13:32.260 --> 00:13:33.470 line:80%
Gotta make this last.

00:13:33.840 --> 00:13:35.100 line:80%
I don't have many left.

00:13:53.640 --> 00:13:54.310 line:80%
Come in.

00:13:56.560 --> 00:13:58.830 line:80%
He's the counselor in the army
and your manager back at the shop.

00:13:58.830 --> 00:13:59.710 line:80%
Talking to him like that—

00:13:59.710 --> 00:14:01.840 line:80%
aren't you afraid he'll hold a grudge?

00:14:02.950 --> 00:14:04.760 line:80%
There's so much to handle in the army.

00:14:04.760 --> 00:14:07.360 line:80%
We can't be bothered
with so many formalities.

00:14:08.400 --> 00:14:09.120 line:80%
Right?

00:14:10.040 --> 00:14:10.670 line:80%
Yes.

00:14:10.720 --> 00:14:12.380 line:80%
Military affairs come first.

00:14:13.400 --> 00:14:14.670 line:80%
Then you two take your time.

00:14:14.670 --> 00:14:16.000 line:80%
I'll go boil some water.

00:14:24.440 --> 00:14:25.440 line:80%
Our plan worked?

00:14:26.200 --> 00:14:29.200 line:80%
I heard you received an urgent dispatch
from Lucheng.

00:14:30.470 --> 00:14:33.590 line:80%
Lord Changxin is likely assembling
his main forces—

00:14:34.980 --> 00:14:37.910 line:80%
probably planning to end this quickly.

00:14:38.800 --> 00:14:40.280 line:80%
Shi Yue and the rebels

00:14:40.280 --> 00:14:42.480 line:80%
fired arrows at Sui Yuanqing
without restraint.

00:14:42.480 --> 00:14:44.610 line:80%
That changes the value of the hostage.

00:14:45.310 --> 00:14:46.820 line:80%
Before, they held back for fear of
hurting the hostage,

00:14:46.820 --> 00:14:49.330 line:80%
so we could stall 30,000 troops
with just 1,000.

00:14:49.330 --> 00:14:50.790 line:80%
But from what we saw today,

00:14:52.000 --> 00:14:53.000 line:80%
this hostage

00:14:53.710 --> 00:14:55.040 line:80%
is no longer worth much.

00:14:56.430 --> 00:14:57.470 line:80%
It seems...

00:14:59.080 --> 00:15:00.550 line:80%
a big battle is imminent.

00:15:06.530 --> 00:15:07.260 line:80%
Yue,

00:15:07.540 --> 00:15:09.350 line:80%
the Heir Apparent already said it—

00:15:09.350 --> 00:15:10.920 line:80%
he told us not to worry about his life

00:15:10.920 --> 00:15:12.920 line:80%
and just charge forward as planned!

00:15:13.920 --> 00:15:15.830 line:80%
But he is the Heir Apparent.

00:15:16.880 --> 00:15:19.120 line:80%
How can we just ignore him?

00:15:19.430 --> 00:15:20.590 line:80%
In today's battle,

00:15:20.800 --> 00:15:23.190 line:80%
that sword strike just happened to
injure him, of all people.

00:15:23.190 --> 00:15:24.670 line:80%
You and I both know his temper—

00:15:24.670 --> 00:15:25.670 line:80%
he seeks revenge
for the smallest grievance

00:15:25.670 --> 00:15:27.000 line:80%
and flares up easily!

00:15:27.160 --> 00:15:28.400 line:80%
I'm afraid he won't

00:15:29.310 --> 00:15:31.510 line:80%
let today's matter go so easily.

00:15:31.950 --> 00:15:33.190 line:80%
You mean...

00:15:33.710 --> 00:15:34.970 line:80%
after all this is over,

00:15:35.400 --> 00:15:36.860 line:80%
he won't let us off easily?

00:15:39.100 --> 00:15:39.930 line:80%
Yue,

00:15:40.520 --> 00:15:42.310 line:80%
the Lord's orders are absolute!

00:15:42.310 --> 00:15:43.670 line:80%
If we mess this up,

00:15:44.190 --> 00:15:46.320 line:80%
our lives are forfeit either way, Yue!

00:15:47.920 --> 00:15:50.250 line:80%
If anything happens to the Heir Apparent,

00:15:51.280 --> 00:15:53.680 line:80%
even if we succeed
in the Lord's grand plan,

00:15:54.120 --> 00:15:56.580 line:80%
once the Heir Apparent
inherits the throne,

00:15:57.190 --> 00:15:59.520 line:80%
I'm afraid neither of us
will have it easy.

00:16:00.120 --> 00:16:02.070 line:80%
We can't shake the blame now.

00:16:03.280 --> 00:16:05.070 line:80%
Yue, stop hesitating.

00:16:05.160 --> 00:16:06.240 line:80%
Make a decision!

00:16:09.470 --> 00:16:10.350 line:80%
Fine.

00:16:11.710 --> 00:16:13.640 line:80%
Tomorrow we launch a full assault.

00:16:16.350 --> 00:16:18.550 line:80%
It would be best
if we could rescue the Heir Apparent.

00:16:18.550 --> 00:16:19.990 line:80%
If not,

00:16:20.760 --> 00:16:23.120 line:80%
we'll take Xie Zheng's head

00:16:23.640 --> 00:16:25.710 line:80%
back to the Lord.

00:16:28.640 --> 00:16:30.040 line:80%
What are you doing?

00:16:31.160 --> 00:16:33.360 line:80%
What can't you say in front of everyone?

00:16:34.800 --> 00:16:36.160 line:80%
Why so secretive?

00:16:37.710 --> 00:16:38.470 line:80%
Sister,

00:16:39.190 --> 00:16:41.250 line:80%
I heard there's a battle in a few days.

00:16:42.090 --> 00:16:45.440 line:80%
This is all the money
I've saved since joining the army.

00:16:45.790 --> 00:16:46.770 line:80%
There's also some money

00:16:46.770 --> 00:16:49.450 line:80%
Big Brother gave me
back in the gambling den.

00:16:49.680 --> 00:16:51.590 line:80%
Please keep it for me, Sister.

00:16:54.640 --> 00:16:56.120 line:80%
Why not ask your big brother to keep it

00:16:56.120 --> 00:16:57.040 line:80%
instead of me?

00:16:57.180 --> 00:16:58.940 line:80%
He's going to battle too.

00:16:59.830 --> 00:17:01.610 line:80%
You don't have to fight.

00:17:02.050 --> 00:17:04.040 line:80%
It's safest with you.

00:17:05.520 --> 00:17:07.350 line:80%
Blades don't discriminate.

00:17:07.869 --> 00:17:10.070 line:80%
If I die on the battlefield,

00:17:11.000 --> 00:17:13.000 line:80%
please take this money

00:17:13.310 --> 00:17:15.190 line:80%
home to my younger sister.

00:17:19.480 --> 00:17:21.110 line:80%
-Alright, alright.
-You're going to be the death of me.

00:17:21.110 --> 00:17:22.680 line:80%
Who told you to say such unlucky things?

00:17:22.680 --> 00:17:23.830 line:80%
All this talk about dying...

00:17:23.830 --> 00:17:24.960 line:80%
Don't say it again.

00:17:26.280 --> 00:17:27.389 line:80%
Who am I?

00:17:28.480 --> 00:17:30.800 line:80%
Since I could
bring you all out here safely,

00:17:30.800 --> 00:17:32.800 line:80%
I can bring you all back home safely.

00:17:33.290 --> 00:17:34.830 line:80%
None of you will be left behind.

00:17:34.830 --> 00:17:35.830 line:80%
Keep it yourself.

00:17:36.520 --> 00:17:37.780 line:80%
If you leave it with me,

00:17:38.150 --> 00:17:39.280 line:80%
when I go back to Lin'an,

00:17:39.280 --> 00:17:40.800 line:80%
I'll spend it all on pigs.

00:17:41.000 --> 00:17:42.930 line:80%
I won't leave a single coin for you.

00:17:45.680 --> 00:17:48.340 line:80%
Then... I'm willing to
buy pigs for you, Sister.

00:17:51.290 --> 00:17:52.380 line:80%
Go to sleep.

00:17:52.960 --> 00:17:54.960 line:80%
Stop thinking about this nonsense.

00:17:57.200 --> 00:17:58.310 line:80%
Got it, Sister.

00:18:24.720 --> 00:18:27.800 line:80%
[Xie]

00:18:25.240 --> 00:18:26.440 line:80%
All units, assemble!

00:18:29.270 --> 00:18:30.400 line:80%
Keep up!

00:18:34.830 --> 00:18:35.960 line:80%
Move! Move!

00:18:43.350 --> 00:18:44.630 line:80%
Stay close, everyone.

00:19:01.110 --> 00:19:02.320 line:80%
Headmaster Gongsun,

00:19:02.550 --> 00:19:04.750 line:80%
are preparations for this campaign...

00:19:05.130 --> 00:19:06.550 line:80%
in order?

00:19:08.240 --> 00:19:09.040 line:80%
Rest assured.

00:19:09.260 --> 00:19:11.000 line:80%
Everything has been arranged properly.

00:19:11.000 --> 00:19:12.400 line:80%
There's no need to worry.

00:19:16.870 --> 00:19:17.870 line:80%
Your Highness...

00:19:19.640 --> 00:19:21.280 line:80%
I must depart now.

00:19:43.010 --> 00:19:44.190 line:80%
Take this Go manual

00:19:44.550 --> 00:19:45.480 line:80%
and keep it safe.

00:19:48.290 --> 00:19:53.550 line:80%
[The Mystery of Qi]

00:19:49.280 --> 00:19:52.280 line:80%
When I was young,
I read a fragment of a Go manual

00:19:52.520 --> 00:19:54.240 line:80%
called "The Mystery of Qi."

00:19:54.480 --> 00:19:55.550 line:80%
As for this book,

00:19:55.800 --> 00:19:57.350 line:80%
there is actually a complete volume

00:19:57.350 --> 00:19:58.880 line:80%
in my family's collection.

00:19:59.390 --> 00:20:02.120 line:80%
Unfortunately,
it's my grandfather's treasure

00:20:02.310 --> 00:20:03.350 line:80%
and cannot be lent out.

00:20:02.370 --> 00:20:04.990 line:80%
[The Mystery of Qi]

00:20:08.150 --> 00:20:10.880 line:80%
On the battlefield,
blades don't discriminate.

00:20:12.520 --> 00:20:14.580 line:80%
Headmaster, please take extra care.

00:20:16.630 --> 00:20:18.390 line:80%
With so many soldiers of the Xie family

00:20:18.390 --> 00:20:19.310 line:80%
protecting me,

00:20:19.310 --> 00:20:20.590 line:80%
I'll surely be fine.

00:20:21.040 --> 00:20:22.310 line:80%
Besides, if I can't beat them,

00:20:22.310 --> 00:20:23.520 line:80%
I'll just run away...

00:20:32.390 --> 00:20:33.590 line:80%
I will wait for you...

00:20:34.720 --> 00:20:35.830 line:80%
to return safely.

00:21:04.410 --> 00:21:08.010 line:80%
[Xie]

00:21:05.680 --> 00:21:07.240 line:80%
Brave men of Great Yin,

00:21:08.470 --> 00:21:09.360 line:80%
you too...

00:21:10.190 --> 00:21:12.150 line:80%
must all return safely.

00:21:16.030 --> 00:21:16.720 line:80%
Your Lordship,

00:21:16.720 --> 00:21:19.150 line:80%
the vanguard has gone with the Counselor
to deploy the formation.

00:21:19.150 --> 00:21:20.350 line:80%
Last night, the rebels

00:21:20.350 --> 00:21:22.550 line:80%
already secretly set up some ambushes.

00:21:23.070 --> 00:21:24.270 line:80%
Depart immediately.

00:21:24.310 --> 00:21:25.350 line:80%
Once the enemy enters the trap,

00:21:25.350 --> 00:21:26.720 line:80%
we'll press the attack and pursue.

00:21:26.720 --> 00:21:27.450 line:80%
Understood.

00:21:29.200 --> 00:21:30.060 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:21:31.630 --> 00:21:32.760 line:80%
Mrs. Fan is coming.

00:21:34.150 --> 00:21:34.960 line:80%
You go ahead.

00:21:34.960 --> 00:21:35.760 line:80%
I'll follow shortly.

00:21:35.760 --> 00:21:36.310 line:80%
Yes.

00:21:36.660 --> 00:21:37.220 line:80%
Yes.

00:21:38.870 --> 00:21:39.960 line:80%
General Wu.

00:21:40.200 --> 00:21:41.110 line:80%
General Jiu.

00:21:41.350 --> 00:21:41.960 line:80%
Madam.

00:21:51.070 --> 00:21:52.870 line:80%
Your wounds are still bleeding.

00:21:53.110 --> 00:21:54.440 line:80%
Just some small injuries.

00:21:54.440 --> 00:21:55.350 line:80%
It's nothing.

00:22:02.520 --> 00:22:03.180 line:80%
Let me do it.

00:22:12.310 --> 00:22:22.260 line:80%
♪ In gold-thread dress,
with moth or willow ornaments ♪

00:22:21.040 --> 00:22:21.830 line:80%
Yan Zheng.

00:22:23.100 --> 00:22:32.650 line:80%
♪ Giggling, she melts into the throng
with trails of scents ♪

00:22:23.660 --> 00:22:24.790 line:80%
How about

00:22:25.310 --> 00:22:27.370 line:80%
I go to the battlefield in your place?

00:22:27.390 --> 00:22:29.200 line:80%
Don't be silly.

00:22:33.100 --> 00:22:34.630 line:80%
Your injuries haven't fully healed yet.

00:22:33.350 --> 00:22:38.330 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:22:34.960 --> 00:22:37.440 line:80%
You won't even be able to lift a blade.

00:22:38.350 --> 00:22:42.950 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:22:39.000 --> 00:22:40.260 line:80%
What would you do then?

00:22:43.990 --> 00:22:46.010 line:80%
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

00:22:44.390 --> 00:22:46.270 line:80%
I'm just a foot soldier
in the infantry battalion.

00:22:46.270 --> 00:22:47.680 line:80%
My job is just to clean up the battlefield

00:22:46.500 --> 00:22:49.470 line:80%
♪ I find her there ♪

00:22:47.680 --> 00:22:49.210 line:80%
and deal with the remnants.

00:22:49.830 --> 00:22:50.800 line:80%
It's not dangerous.

00:22:50.200 --> 00:22:55.260 line:80%
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

00:22:54.310 --> 00:22:55.550 line:80%
Then be careful.

00:22:55.710 --> 00:22:59.750 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:22:59.780 --> 00:23:04.980 line:80%
♪ But in the crowd once and again
I look for her in vain ♪

00:23:03.000 --> 00:23:04.330 line:80%
Wait for me to come back.

00:23:05.460 --> 00:23:07.660 line:80%
♪ When all at once I turn my head ♪

00:23:07.970 --> 00:23:12.380 line:80%
♪ I find her there ♪

00:23:13.070 --> 00:23:14.270 line:80%
The herbal medicine will get cold.

00:23:14.270 --> 00:23:22.970 line:80%
♪ Where lantern light is dimly shed ♪

00:23:14.760 --> 00:23:16.690 line:80%
You need to drink it while it's hot.

00:23:29.390 --> 00:23:30.070 line:80%
Okay.

00:23:41.280 --> 00:23:42.040 line:80%
By the way,

00:23:43.000 --> 00:23:45.280 line:80%
which infantry battalion are you in?

00:23:45.720 --> 00:23:47.580 line:80%
Which general do you serve under?

00:23:50.600 --> 00:23:52.800 line:80%
Third Battalion of the Left Guard Army.

00:23:55.630 --> 00:23:57.250 line:80%
Why do you ask?

00:23:57.760 --> 00:23:58.520 line:80%
Nothing.

00:23:59.390 --> 00:24:00.590 line:80%
I was just curious.

00:24:11.240 --> 00:24:12.840 line:80%
If anything happens to me...

00:24:15.110 --> 00:24:16.770 line:80%
take care of Changning for me.

00:24:19.800 --> 00:24:20.630 line:80%
You...

00:24:35.520 --> 00:24:36.280 line:80%
Yan Zheng...

00:24:40.830 --> 00:24:42.760 line:80%
I can't let anything happen to you.

00:24:56.040 --> 00:24:57.150 line:80%
Emergency assembly!

00:24:57.150 --> 00:24:58.150 line:80%
Move! Move! Move!

00:24:58.310 --> 00:24:59.200 line:80%
Assembly!

00:24:59.350 --> 00:25:00.110 line:80%
Hurry!

00:25:21.730 --> 00:25:23.060 line:80%
Wait for me to come back.

00:25:29.910 --> 00:25:30.590 line:80%
Here.

00:25:31.440 --> 00:25:32.110 line:80%
Changning,

00:25:32.600 --> 00:25:34.110 line:80%
remember what I told you.

00:26:14.350 --> 00:26:15.080 line:80%
Big Brother,

00:26:15.470 --> 00:26:16.360 line:80%
Sister.

00:26:22.630 --> 00:26:23.550 line:80%
What are you doing here?

00:26:23.550 --> 00:26:24.720 line:80%
Yeah, Sister. Why are you here?

00:26:24.720 --> 00:26:25.870 line:80%
What are you trying to pull?

00:26:25.870 --> 00:26:28.190 line:80%
Sister, please go back.

00:26:28.350 --> 00:26:29.480 line:80%
The battlefield is brutal—

00:26:29.480 --> 00:26:30.720 line:80%
you could die at any moment.

00:26:30.720 --> 00:26:32.480 line:80%
Have you forgotten the dam flood?

00:26:32.480 --> 00:26:33.280 line:80%
I remember.

00:26:33.520 --> 00:26:35.650 line:80%
That's why I can't let Yan Zheng fight.

00:26:35.960 --> 00:26:37.040 line:80%
I drugged him.

00:26:37.110 --> 00:26:38.170 line:80%
If I don't take his place,

00:26:38.170 --> 00:26:39.480 line:80%
he'll truly be marked as a deserter.

00:26:39.480 --> 00:26:39.960 line:80%
You...

00:26:40.870 --> 00:26:42.480 line:80%
Why are you so protective of him?

00:26:42.480 --> 00:26:44.240 line:80%
Why don't you think more about yourself?

00:26:44.240 --> 00:26:45.340 line:80%
We're going to war!

00:26:45.480 --> 00:26:46.520 line:80%
Exactly.

00:26:46.720 --> 00:26:47.830 line:80%
I know it's war.

00:26:49.000 --> 00:26:50.800 line:80%
I'm just going to fill the ranks.

00:26:51.110 --> 00:26:52.870 line:80%
Once we're on the battlefield,

00:26:52.870 --> 00:26:53.760 line:80%
we'll find a chance to cut

00:26:53.760 --> 00:26:55.460 line:80%
the ears off a corpse.

00:26:55.760 --> 00:26:57.520 line:80%
That way, even if our superiors find out,

00:26:57.520 --> 00:26:59.830 line:80%
we can prove we fought and killed enemies.

00:26:59.830 --> 00:27:01.000 line:80%
It's not that easy.

00:27:01.040 --> 00:27:02.200 line:80%
It's not that easy!

00:27:02.630 --> 00:27:03.480 line:80%
Let me ask you,

00:27:03.480 --> 00:27:04.240 line:80%
which one of you has actually been
on a battlefield?

00:27:04.240 --> 00:27:04.960 line:80%
Never.

00:27:04.960 --> 00:27:07.420 line:80%
-It's far too dangerous!
-What's the noise?

00:27:08.110 --> 00:27:08.940 line:80%
You lot,

00:27:09.110 --> 00:27:10.440 line:80%
which squad are you from?

00:27:10.440 --> 00:27:12.000 line:80%
Why are you in my unit?

00:27:13.590 --> 00:27:15.150 line:80%
We're from the Third Battalion

00:27:15.150 --> 00:27:18.480 line:80%
of the Left Guard Army,
responsible for clearing remnants.

00:27:18.520 --> 00:27:19.520 line:80%
Third Battalion?

00:27:19.720 --> 00:27:20.910 line:80%
Left Guard Army?

00:27:21.040 --> 00:27:22.830 line:80%
Since when do we have a Third Battalion?

00:27:22.830 --> 00:27:24.890 line:80%
We only have the Vanguard Battalion!

00:27:25.110 --> 00:27:26.150 line:80%
You little rascals,

00:27:26.150 --> 00:27:27.480 line:80%
you're not impostors, are you?

00:27:27.480 --> 00:27:28.830 line:80%
Watch your mouth!

00:27:28.830 --> 00:27:30.070 line:80%
The army is about to move out!

00:27:30.070 --> 00:27:31.330 line:80%
What's all this noise?

00:27:32.040 --> 00:27:32.720 line:80%
General Wu.

00:27:33.310 --> 00:27:34.280 line:80%
They...

00:27:38.510 --> 00:27:39.070 line:80%
You...

00:27:47.200 --> 00:27:47.830 line:80%
Attention, everyone!

00:27:47.830 --> 00:27:48.520 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:27:48.520 --> 00:27:49.310 line:80%
Fall in!

00:27:50.280 --> 00:27:51.280 line:80%
General Wu,

00:27:51.520 --> 00:27:53.380 line:80%
my husband is seriously injured.

00:27:53.550 --> 00:27:55.310 line:80%
For the sake of comradeship,

00:27:55.420 --> 00:27:57.420 line:80%
please pretend you don't know this.

00:27:57.470 --> 00:27:58.670 line:80%
When I return from battle,

00:27:58.670 --> 00:27:59.990 line:80%
having earned merits,

00:28:00.390 --> 00:28:02.440 line:80%
it won't matter even if they want to
hold Yan Zheng accountable.

00:28:02.440 --> 00:28:03.100 line:80%
His Lord...

00:28:05.110 --> 00:28:06.710 line:80%
Your husband agreed to this?

00:28:07.760 --> 00:28:08.760 line:80%
I drugged him.

00:28:08.760 --> 00:28:09.310 line:80%
You...

00:28:10.630 --> 00:28:11.800 line:80%
How can you be so reckless?

00:28:11.800 --> 00:28:12.720 line:80%
Do you even know

00:28:12.870 --> 00:28:14.730 line:80%
how vital he is to today's battle?

00:28:14.830 --> 00:28:16.110 line:80%
He's not even a squad leader.

00:28:16.110 --> 00:28:17.440 line:80%
How important can he be?

00:28:17.530 --> 00:28:19.440 line:80%
At best, he'll just kill
a few more enemies.

00:28:19.440 --> 00:28:20.390 line:80%
In his current condition,

00:28:20.390 --> 00:28:22.040 line:80%
he's not even stronger than me.

00:28:22.040 --> 00:28:22.630 line:80%
Where is he?

00:28:22.630 --> 00:28:23.280 line:80%
I'm going to find him.

00:28:23.280 --> 00:28:24.110 line:80%
It's too late.

00:28:24.630 --> 00:28:26.800 line:80%
That knockout drug is quite strong.

00:28:27.000 --> 00:28:28.390 line:80%
He'll be out for a long time.

00:28:28.390 --> 00:28:29.590 line:80%
Whoa!

00:28:30.310 --> 00:28:31.630 line:80%
Shi Yue has led his men and torn

00:28:31.630 --> 00:28:32.720 line:80%
a gap through the vanguard.

00:28:32.720 --> 00:28:33.800 line:80%
By order of the Counselor:

00:28:33.800 --> 00:28:35.480 line:80%
the Left Guard Army is to
reinforce them immediately!

00:28:35.480 --> 00:28:36.000 line:80%
Hyah!

00:28:41.040 --> 00:28:42.380 line:80%
Left flank of the Vanguard Battalion—
attention!

00:28:42.380 --> 00:28:43.040 line:80%
-Sir!
-Sir!

00:28:43.150 --> 00:28:44.310 line:80%
Full-speed march!

00:28:44.310 --> 00:28:45.510 line:80%
-Yes, sir!
-Yes, sir!

00:28:49.000 --> 00:28:50.680 line:80%
You, go to the right flank reserve unit.

00:28:50.680 --> 00:28:51.550 line:80%
You few,

00:28:52.390 --> 00:28:53.280 line:80%
protect her well.

00:28:53.280 --> 00:28:54.040 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:28:56.760 --> 00:28:57.870 line:80%
Go notify His Lordship immediately.

00:28:57.870 --> 00:29:00.930 line:80%
Tell him that Her Ladyship
has gone to the battlefield.

00:29:15.550 --> 00:29:16.760 line:80%
Gongsun Yin,

00:29:17.550 --> 00:29:19.000 line:80%
do you dare to come down

00:29:19.110 --> 00:29:20.760 line:80%
and face me in a duel?

00:29:21.280 --> 00:29:22.760 line:80%
I'm but a scholar!

00:29:22.910 --> 00:29:24.520 line:80%
Naturally, I cannot beat you in a fight!

00:29:24.520 --> 00:29:27.830 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an is still waiting to
invite you for tea!

00:29:38.240 --> 00:29:39.240 line:80%
I must say,

00:29:39.440 --> 00:29:42.370 line:80%
Mrs. Fan's way of provoking people
actually works pretty well!

00:29:42.370 --> 00:29:43.990 line:80%
How dare you.

00:29:44.480 --> 00:29:45.350 line:80%
Gongsun Yin,

00:29:46.070 --> 00:29:47.390 line:80%
you coward!

00:29:47.390 --> 00:29:50.250 line:80%
Why don't you come down
and fight me fair and square?

00:29:53.760 --> 00:29:55.000 line:80%
As you wish.

00:30:04.480 --> 00:30:06.210 line:80%
Reserve Battalion, assemble!

00:30:06.390 --> 00:30:07.910 line:80%
Reserve Battalion, assemble!

00:30:07.910 --> 00:30:09.640 line:80%
Reserve Battalion, assemble!

00:30:10.760 --> 00:30:12.350 line:80%
-Hurry!
-Even we have to go to the battlefield.

00:30:12.350 --> 00:30:13.520 line:80%
How bad must the fighting up front be?

00:30:13.520 --> 00:30:15.200 line:80%
Reserve Battalion, assemble!

00:30:15.200 --> 00:30:16.800 line:80%
Hurry, hurry, hurry!

00:30:19.520 --> 00:30:20.520 line:80%
Assemble!

00:30:24.440 --> 00:30:26.840 line:80%
How are we supposed to
fight in this battle?

00:30:27.150 --> 00:30:29.080 line:80%
Let's just focus on staying alive.

00:30:29.960 --> 00:30:30.590 line:80%
Mandi.

00:30:31.070 --> 00:30:32.110 line:80%
Once you're on the battlefield,

00:30:32.110 --> 00:30:33.040 line:80%
stay close to me.

00:30:33.110 --> 00:30:34.090 line:80%
Don't get separated.

00:30:34.090 --> 00:30:36.150 line:80%
If worse comes to worst, hide behind me.

00:30:36.150 --> 00:30:37.110 line:80%
Okay, Sister.

00:30:38.760 --> 00:30:39.960 line:80%
After this battle,

00:30:39.980 --> 00:30:42.240 line:80%
we can go home
and have a good meal, right?

00:30:42.930 --> 00:30:43.990 line:80%
Probably.

00:30:44.590 --> 00:30:45.590 line:80%
Let's stay alive first.

00:30:45.590 --> 00:30:46.520 line:80%
Cut the chatter!

00:30:46.680 --> 00:30:48.540 line:80%
Await orders from the front line!

00:31:03.200 --> 00:31:04.630 line:80%
Look, it's fog!

00:31:29.540 --> 00:31:31.270 line:80%
There's blood mixed in the fog.

00:31:31.950 --> 00:31:33.110 line:80%
All units, on alert!

00:31:33.110 --> 00:31:34.110 line:80%
Draw your blades!

00:33:03.910 --> 00:33:05.280 line:80%
Don't stay where you are!

00:33:05.280 --> 00:33:06.540 line:80%
Charge out!

00:33:07.110 --> 00:33:07.980 line:80%
Go!

00:33:10.760 --> 00:33:13.800 line:80%
Forty-seven, forty-eight,

00:33:14.720 --> 00:33:17.920 line:80%
forty-nine, fifty.

00:33:23.550 --> 00:33:26.520 line:80%
One, two...

00:33:29.630 --> 00:33:32.760 line:80%
Brother-in-Law, why are you awake?

00:33:33.800 --> 00:33:35.720 line:80%
Sister told me to count to 1,000

00:33:35.720 --> 00:33:37.580 line:80%
and then wake you up with a needle.

00:33:37.680 --> 00:33:40.550 line:80%
But I don't know how to count to 1,000.

00:33:40.960 --> 00:33:43.220 line:80%
Sister said that every time I count to 50,

00:33:43.240 --> 00:33:45.230 line:80%
I put down a stone.

00:33:45.590 --> 00:33:48.220 line:80%
I need to collect 20 stones.

00:33:48.310 --> 00:33:50.440 line:80%
How did you wake up so early?

00:33:55.590 --> 00:33:56.960 line:80%
Brother-in-Law.

00:33:59.200 --> 00:34:00.110 line:80%
Xie Jiu.

00:34:02.590 --> 00:34:03.590 line:80%
Xie Jiu!

00:34:04.310 --> 00:34:05.070 line:80%
Xie Jiu!

00:34:06.870 --> 00:34:08.560 line:80%
Your Lordship, here you are.

00:34:08.560 --> 00:34:09.350 line:80%
What happened?

00:34:09.350 --> 00:34:10.310 line:80%
The situation at the front is critical.

00:34:10.310 --> 00:34:12.160 line:80%
Shi Yue has indeed abandoned Sui Yuanqing,

00:34:12.160 --> 00:34:13.680 line:80%
letting Shi Hu slaughter his way through
and open a path.

00:34:13.680 --> 00:34:14.680 line:80%
We can't hold on much longer.

00:34:14.680 --> 00:34:16.470 line:80%
Where is my sister?

00:34:17.160 --> 00:34:18.030 line:80%
Mrs. Fan...

00:34:19.120 --> 00:34:20.269 line:80%
is at the front line.

00:34:28.080 --> 00:34:29.939 line:80%
Your Lordship, are you all right?

00:34:35.820 --> 00:34:37.680 line:80%
Changning, turn around.

00:34:37.680 --> 00:34:38.720 line:80%
Okay.

00:34:40.240 --> 00:34:42.640 line:80%
Five, six,

00:34:43.350 --> 00:34:46.280 line:80%
seven, eight,

00:34:46.800 --> 00:34:49.390 line:80%
nine, ten.

00:34:49.510 --> 00:34:50.760 line:80%
Bring my armor.

00:34:51.030 --> 00:34:51.560 line:80%
Yes.

00:35:41.430 --> 00:35:43.360 line:80%
You've been a good pig in this life.

00:35:43.640 --> 00:35:45.440 line:80%
Be a good person in the next life!

00:35:46.950 --> 00:35:48.240 line:80%
Someone, come over there!

00:35:48.240 --> 00:35:49.910 line:80%
Destroy the catapults!

00:35:53.240 --> 00:35:54.310 line:80%
Don't just stand here.

00:35:54.310 --> 00:35:55.170 line:80%
Let's go fight!

00:35:55.870 --> 00:35:56.400 line:80%
Let's go!

00:35:57.090 --> 00:35:58.710 line:80%
Let's go!

00:35:59.180 --> 00:35:59.960 line:80%
Hyah!

00:36:13.560 --> 00:36:14.360 line:80%
Her Ladyship?

00:37:38.330 --> 00:37:40.200 line:80%
You Yanzhou Army soldiers are so useless—

00:37:40.200 --> 00:37:42.000 line:80%
not a single one of you can fight!

00:37:42.390 --> 00:37:43.440 line:80%
General Wu!

00:37:44.130 --> 00:37:47.190 line:80%
Tell the Marquis of Wu'an to come out
and meet his death!

00:37:48.390 --> 00:37:49.710 line:80%
If you don't take it,

00:37:49.730 --> 00:37:52.330 line:80%
your Heir Apparent
won't have an heir anymore!

00:37:53.510 --> 00:37:56.250 line:80%
You're that woman who insulted
our Heir Apparent that day.

00:37:56.250 --> 00:37:58.250 line:80%
Coming to battle with a small knife?

00:37:58.640 --> 00:38:00.170 line:80%
Who are you looking down on?

00:38:00.470 --> 00:38:02.930 line:80%
I'll smash you into a pulp today!

00:38:10.680 --> 00:38:11.920 line:80%
Fan, are you okay?

00:38:35.430 --> 00:38:36.470 line:80%
Go to hell!

00:39:21.510 --> 00:39:21.820 line:80%
[Sui]

00:40:23.530 --> 00:40:25.360 line:80%
Fan!

00:40:37.870 --> 00:40:40.500 line:80%
Shi Hu is dead! We won!

00:40:41.800 --> 00:40:44.140 line:80%
Shi Hu is dead! We won!

00:40:44.240 --> 00:40:45.870 line:80%
Fan, are you alright?

00:40:46.470 --> 00:40:48.720 line:80%
We won!

00:40:50.600 --> 00:40:52.400 line:80%
Look, it's the Marquis of Wu'an!

00:40:54.950 --> 00:40:56.560 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an is coming!

00:40:56.560 --> 00:40:57.710 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an?

00:40:58.350 --> 00:40:59.550 line:80%
Marquis of Wu'an!

00:40:59.800 --> 00:41:02.690 line:80%
-Marquis of Wu'an!
-Marquis of Wu'an!

00:41:03.030 --> 00:41:05.950 line:80%
-Marquis of Wu'an!
-Marquis of Wu'an!

00:41:06.010 --> 00:41:07.400 line:80%
Doesn't he look like...

00:41:09.340 --> 00:41:10.330 line:80%
A little bit.

00:41:12.030 --> 00:41:13.160 line:80%
Well...

00:41:13.470 --> 00:41:15.800 line:80%
The more I look,
the more he looks like him.

00:41:37.380 --> 00:41:40.050 line:80%
♪ Rain falls to the ground,
who sighs within the temple halls? ♪

00:41:40.680 --> 00:41:43.280 line:80%
♪ Waiting for the wind to rise,
the Emperor upholds great righteousness ♪

00:41:43.670 --> 00:41:46.520 line:80%
♪ How can worldly affairs ever go
as one wishes? ♪

00:41:47.090 --> 00:41:49.720 line:80%
♪ Words may be exhausted,
yet you and I remain inseparable ♪

00:41:50.080 --> 00:41:52.520 line:80%
♪ As the wind scatters,
how can love be proven? ♪

00:41:53.170 --> 00:41:55.860 line:80%
♪ Like rain striking duckweed,
we choose to believe ♪

00:41:56.920 --> 00:41:59.120 line:80%
♪ Crossing borders,
our voices grow more resolute ♪

00:41:59.660 --> 00:42:03.870 line:80%
♪ We hold fast to
our original promise together ♪

00:42:05.030 --> 00:42:07.860 line:80%
♪ I'm cautious about destiny ♪

00:42:08.490 --> 00:42:10.260 line:80%
♪ But I won't give up ♪

00:42:11.510 --> 00:42:14.010 line:80%
♪ But we are always on the battlefield ♪

00:42:14.410 --> 00:42:16.700 line:80%
♪ And meeting among the flames of war ♪

00:42:17.610 --> 00:42:20.750 line:80%
♪ Knowing fierce storms lie ahead ♪

00:42:21.650 --> 00:42:24.550 line:80%
♪ We face them head-on ♪

00:42:25.760 --> 00:42:30.200 line:80%
♪ We persist in reclaiming lost ground ♪

00:42:31.780 --> 00:42:37.370 line:80%
♪ Unafraid of the enemy's attack ♪

00:42:36.830 --> 00:42:38.080 line:80%
Oh no.

00:42:38.730 --> 00:42:41.730 line:80%
♪ Unafraid ♪